@startuml
' Activity swim lane (no Graphviz, no C4 include) of the developer's journey.
' Nodes are tagged with [[ct://el/<alias>]]. Render: scripts/render-diagrams.sh
!theme materia-outline
' Opaque background so the diagram reads on any VS Code editor theme (the panel
' background follows the reader's theme; C4 diagrams bake this automatically).
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
' Roboto is vendored into the renderer image and embedded into the SVG.
skinparam defaultFontName Roboto

title gCodeTour — developer journey

|Developer|
start
:Open a workspace with tours [[ct://el/open]];
:Start a tour [[ct://el/start]];
|Extension|
:Discover .tour files [[ct://el/discover]];
:Render step in a comment thread [[ct://el/render]];
:Show synchronized diagram [[ct://el/diagramstep]];
|Developer|
:Navigate next / previous [[ct://el/navigate]];
stop

@enduml
